<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>기병대 [기병대]</dt><br>
<dd>cavalry; horse troop</dd><br>
<dd>말을 타고 싸우는 병사로 조직한 군대.</dd><br>
<dd>The troop consisting of soldiers who fight on horses.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>기병 [기병]</dt><br>
